## Context: Cognitive Load in Team Topologies

Three load types: intrinsic (domain complexity), extraneous (tooling, cross-team coordination), germane (learning — the "good" load).
When total load exceeds capacity: quality degrades, delivery slows, burnout increases.
High interaction counts (especially collaboration mode) add extraneous load.

